B.Rg=new A.d7("Optional fields not labelled as optional","Photo upload and several profile fields were effectively optional but were not marked as such, leading users to believe they had to complete them to proceed.",B.eh,"3.3.2 Labels or Instructions","Optional fields labelled explicitly as \u201cOptional \u2014 you can add this later\u201d. Skip affordances added where relevant.")
