B.RK=new A.dg("Standardised all interactive component styles to a single consistent token set","The heuristic audit found at least four distinct button styles and three different expansion panel treatments \u2014 all inconsistent with each other and the wider brand.","Consistency restored across buttons, tooltips, modals, and toggle states. Engineering noted lower maintenance cost as a secondary benefit.",B.bE)
